  "description_snippet": "This is a dupe of 681761. I rewrote it to follow the security template, sorry :).  \n  \n**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nDuring Array.concat() the `visitor` variable is created which is what is returned after the function is complete. The type of the `visitor` variable is determined by the first argument"
